data.title: Zantedeschia elliottiana / Yellow Calla Lily
data.meta_description: - This is a yellow flowering selection that is not normally seen growing in the garden, but is a popular cutflower that lasts a long time in water.  Provide a fertile, moist, well drained soil and filtered sunlight for the best growing conditions.  This selection can also be grown in a container as an accent plant because of its striking, glossy, coarse-textured foliage.
